      <details>
        <summary>Who is Cavalry Portfolio Services?</summary>
        <p>Cavalry Portfolio Services is a prominent debt collection agency and debt buyer. They purchase portfolios of defaulted debt from original creditors, such as banks and credit card companies, at a fraction of the face value, and then attempt to collect the full amount from consumers.</p>
      </details>
